Nutrient data for: TERRY'S ALL GOLD CHOCOLATE PIECES-ASSORTED DARK, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 03664346304894

Ingredients: Sugar, cocoa mass, vegetable fats (palm, shea), cocoa butter, MILK fat, whole MILK powder, glucose syrup, marzipan (sugar, ALMONDS, humectant (sorbitol), glucose syrup, stabiliser (invertase)), invert sugar syrup, HAZELNUTS, whey powder (from MILK), skimmed MILK powder, HAZELNUT paste, humectants (sorbitol, glycerol), reduced fat cocoa powder, emulsifiers (SOYA lecithin, E442, sunflower lecithin), whey permeate powder (from MILK), freeze-dried strawberry powder, ethanol, flavourings, stabiliser (invertase), lactose (from MILK), acidity regulator (citric acid).
